@startuml Deployment_01_HighLevel

title Deployment-Diagramm Teil 1 - High-Level Übersicht

package "Client Schicht" {
    node "Browser (Student/Admin)" as CLIENT {
        component "HTML5/CSS3/JavaScript" as FRONTEND
    }
}

package "Webserver Schicht" {
    node "Tomcat 8.5 / 11" as TOMCAT {
        artifact "wissentest.war" as WAR
    }
}

package "Datenbankserver Schicht" {
    node "PostgreSQL 15" as DB {
        database "wissentest" as WISSENTEST_DB
    }
}

package "Konfiguration" {
    artifact "db.properties" as DB_PROPS
    artifact "web.xml" as WEB_XML
    artifact "pom.xml" as POM
}

' Verbindungen
CLIENT --> TOMCAT : "HTTP(S)\nPort 8080/8443"
TOMCAT --> DB : "JDBC/TCP\nPort 5432"

TOMCAT -.-> DB_PROPS : "Liest"
TOMCAT -.-> WEB_XML : "Verwendet"
TOMCAT -.-> POM : "Gebaut mit"

note right of CLIENT
  **Client-Technologien:**
  - HTML5 DOM
  - CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid)
  - Vanilla JavaScript
  - Fetch API / AJAX
  - Session Cookies
end note

note right of TOMCAT
  **Tomcat Server:**
  - Java 17 JVM
  - WAR-Deployment
  - Port 8080 (HTTP)
  - Port 8443 (HTTPS)
  - Context: /wissentest
end note

note right of DB
  **PostgreSQL Datenbank:**
  - Host: localhost:5432
  - Database: wissentest
  - User: student
  - Connection Pool: HikariCP
  - 8 Tabellen
  - Indexes & Constraints
end note

@enduml
